309
00:20:23,020 --> 00:20:25,220
Let me see him! I'm begging you!

310
00:20:27,360 --> 00:20:28,380
On your feet.

311
00:20:31,500 --> 00:20:32,620
Come with us.

312
00:20:45,800 --> 00:20:47,440
When we interrogate people,

